phases.prompt:
Create implementation tickets for epic {{epic.id}}: {{epic.name}}

Description: {{epic.description}}

Break this epic into small, actionable tickets. Each ticket should be completable in a single coding session.

Create {{state_dir}}/epics/{{epic.id}}/tickets.json with structure:
[
  {
    "id": "T001",
    "title": "Short title",
    "description": "Detailed description of what to implement",
    "acceptance_criteria": ["Criterion 1", "Criterion 2"],
    "status": "pending"
  }
]

Order tickets by implementation dependency.

Implement ticket {{ticket.id}}: {{ticket.title}}

Description: {{ticket.description}}

Acceptance Criteria:
{{ticket.acceptance_criteria}}

Write the code needed to complete this ticket. Document what you implemented in {{state_dir}}/epics/{{epic.id}}/tickets/{{ticket.id}}/implementation.md including:
1. Files modified/created
2. Key implementation decisions
3. Any assumptions made

